Methods, Models, and GIS
Toward Open Source Kenya: Creating and Sharing a GIS Database of Nairobi
Sarah Williams Department of Urban Studies and Planning , Massachusetts Institute of Technology , Elizabeth Marcello Center for Sustainable Urban Development , Earth Institute, Columbia University & Jacqueline M. Klopp Center for Sustainable Urban Development , Earth Institute, Columbia University
Pages 114-130 | Received 01 Jul 2011, Accepted 01 Jun 2013, Published online: 20 Nov 2013
Pages 114-130
